stals free of\nferromagnetic spurious phases can be obtained by remelting samples with nominal\n$\\delta$=0.05 in a Bridgman process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 19:10:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
