 physics-based heuristic approach in terms of demand error,\nwhile, contrary to the heuristic, our method prolongs the lifetime of high-risk\nturbines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 20:12:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-21"}
