 to discover life in the cosmos. These stars are\nthe best path towards the discovery of habitable planets using the TESS mission\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 23:38:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
